@ModelImportedVariable(name="externalSolarIrradiance", type=java.lang.Double.class) @ModelExportedVariable(name="currentPowerProducedSolarPanel", type=java.lang.Double.class) public class SolarPanelElectricityModel extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.AtomicHIOA
The class SolarPanelElectricityModel defines a simulation model for the electricity production of the SOlar Panel.

Description

The electric power production (in Wats) depends upon the sunshine (solar radiation) of the day.

Initially, the electric power production is at 0.0 W.

  • Imported events: none
  • Exported events: none
  • Imported variables: none
  • Exported variables: name = currentPowerProducedSolarPanel, type = Double
